  "description_snippet": "Chrome on iOS uses WebKit as its engine, so I use WebKit with ASan to more easily reproduce this vulnerability.\n\n## Reproduce\n\n1.Download WebKit\n```cpp\ngit clone https://github.com/Webkit/WebKit\n```\n\n2.Build WebKit with ASAN(or not)\n```cpp\n./Tools/Scripts/set-webkit-configuration --release --asan\n./"
